    "Name": "Scimitar HCV",
    "Details": "This 3050 upgrade to the Scimitar does not use the standard autocannon. In its place are a TAG spotting laser, twin SRM-4, and a Narc Missile Beacon launcher. The remaining ton is added to the armor plating. The Scimitar Medium Hover Tank is very similar to the Saracen. Following the success of that combat vehicle, Scarborough Limited designed another pair of tanks with the same chassis to capitalize on sales. Their plan was successful, and Scarborough had another hit on their hands, five years after the release of the Saracen.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: This unit can not deploy in Lunar or Martian biomes due to using an ICE.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 8/12 hexes / 240/360 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       190     20\n<b>Left</b>         130     20\n<b>Right</b>       130     20\n<b>Rear</b>        100     20\n<b>Turret</b>      135     20\n\n<b>Total</b>      685    100</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Rugged</color>",
